summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 to 5 inclusive, Block 14, Fauntleroy Addition, and a portion of Govt. Lots 2 and 3, Section 35, Township 24 North, Range East., W. M. and Second Class Tide Lands adjoining, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-154 and 17-112, respectively.
